Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.70,0:00:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,When I saw people wearing black, I got the feeling that we were all heading towards the same place
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.60,0:00:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a strange yet familiar feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.61,0:00:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like being a kid inside a bus while heading to the public pool,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.58,0:00:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,feeling that everyone around me is also going to the pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.65,0:00:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That sensation
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.16,0:00:52.20,Title,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fad(1000,0)\frz19.19\pos(1093.334,577)}Ari no Koto{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.54,0:01:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I was part of a 5-member idol group
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.34,0:01:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The group's name was Udagawa White Bears
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.44,0:01:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It was often teased for sounding like a boys baseball team
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.18,0:01:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a year since disbandment
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.50,0:01:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We weren't really that popular anyways
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.01,0:01:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Our center's withdrawal decided our fate
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.32,0:01:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Us that were left behind tried our best to continue for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.89,0:01:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,but the final live went in shambles and ended miserably.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.79,0:01:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ari!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.53,0:01:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,, It's been awhile! Doing well?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.97,0:01:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Looks like Sumi took the same train
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.87,0:01:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I made a mistake and just rushed in the train
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.47,0:01:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.68,0:01:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow you look like an adult now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.85,0:01:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.60,0:01:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't changed at all though
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.45,0:01:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's because you're wearing black
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.73,0:01:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So are you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.60,0:01:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.22,0:01:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been awhile!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.55,0:01:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been awhile
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.35,0:01:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for being late
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.69,0:01:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. It's nice to see you both of you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.32,0:02:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you been well?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.12,0:02:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a safety pin?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.62,0:02:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Her blazer got a rip on the back
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.87,0:02:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable right? It's been so long and she tears her clothes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.47,0:02:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,How did this even happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.17,0:02:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, I just rode the train as usual though
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.88,0:02:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought one with me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.78,0:02:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.98,0:02:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So Samu lived in this kind of area
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.95,0:02:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's way off where you'd expect Samu to live right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.25,0:02:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.76,0:02:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.89,0:02:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's ride a taxi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.21,0:02:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I say that but there seems to be none
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.50,0:02:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like we can walk it though\N-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.15,0:02:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I searched it up awhile ago and it's around 15 minutes away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.40,0:02:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,As expected of you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.37,0:02:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems to be that way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.07,0:02:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's head that way\N-Let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.92,0:02:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just pitch black
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.74,0:02:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing in sight at all
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.71,0:02:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already late after all
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.00,0:02:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The names we go may be weird to others
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.58,0:02:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But they come from parts of our names
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.11,0:02:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Arimoto, hence Ari
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.50,0:02:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sumi is Hasumi
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.69,0:03:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Kimu is Kimura
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.49,0:03:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Momo is Momoko
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.50,0:03:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But Samu is the only exception
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.63,0:03:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though the name Ito Chika does not contain "samu" anywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.73,0:03:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,but for some reason, we called her Samu
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.30,0:03:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That Samu, 2 days ago
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.14,0:03:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,on the way home from buying something
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.50,0:03:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,got hit by a truck and passed away
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.51,0:03:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We were lucky we found a taxi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.45,0:03:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would've known that we were going the wrong way
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.68,0:03:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.00,0:03:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What happens again in funerals?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.36,0:03:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a wake, not a funeral
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.39,0:03:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know either way
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.16,0:03:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,First light an incense, and then give the family your condolences
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.36,0:03:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What exactly do I have to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.27,0:03:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We learned of her death only last night
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.04,0:03:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So everyone looked for clothes in a rush,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.57,0:03:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,not having any mourning dresses at hand, it was really rude
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.88,0:03:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't the cabinet smell bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.38,0:03:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.95,0:04:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I just borrowed this from my mom
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.05,0:04:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a big shoulder pad inside
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.99,0:04:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you Hirano Nora?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.69,0:04:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But actually my clothes aren't even black, just navy blue
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.56,0:04:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Will it be noticed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.59,0:04:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's night so it should be fine
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.60,0:04:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ari's clothes look cute right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.07,0:04:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I bought it for when my relative had a wedding
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.14,0:04:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if this is too flashy
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.84,0:04:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that fine? It shows your grievance for the family
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.91,0:04:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a loose thread at the back of your stockings though
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.28,0:04:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.05,0:04:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are your clothes so easy to tear?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.65,0:04:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,How much will you put in the {\i1}goshugi{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.65,0:04:36.20,TL Note,,0,0,0,,{\pos(962.1,92.4)}TL note: {\i1}goshugi{\i0} is an envelope with money, given as gifts in weddings\N{\i1}okoden{\i0} is the proper term for condolence money
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.25,0:04:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not {\i1}goshugi{\i0}. it's {\i1}okoden{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.32,0:04:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm giving 20,000
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.35,0:04:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I only put in 10,000
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.62,0:04:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Also it's bad to have the first number be divisible by 2
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.86,0:04:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's {\i1}goshugi{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.39,0:04:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, recently having it at 2 is like saying "Best of wishes to the both of you"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.70,0:04:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I already told you, that's for {\i1}goshugi{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.14,0:05:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't be accepting any offerings
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.14,0:05:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But....even if you say that
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.38,0:05:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Your thoughts and feelings are enough
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.60,0:05:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll guide you inside
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.23,0:05:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like we've earned something
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.10,0:05:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you use it to repair your phone's screen
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.04,0:05:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Komiyama-san came by
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.80,0:05:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.24,0:05:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean for a manager, Komiyama-san is a no-show when he's needed
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.29,0:05:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be calling them over, so please wait here
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.40,0:05:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Onii-san, it looks like Chika's friends are here to see her
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming all the way out here today on such a short notice
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.54,0:06:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Please go ahead and light some incense
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.68,0:06:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Samu's wake is empty
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.91,0:06:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We probably came too late that's why everyone's already gone but,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.25,0:06:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,even though we are lamenting the death of Samu,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.65,0:06:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,the emptiness just doesn't feel right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.35,0:07:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all from Udagawa White Bears right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.60,0:07:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.22,0:07:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming despite your busy schedules
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.63,0:07:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Please go take a look at her face
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.41,0:07:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,, Samu's.....already dead
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.95,0:07:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to put something for her to be buried with, is it fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.85,0:08:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as it is something that can be burned
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.36,0:08:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Samu liked this after all
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.01,0:08:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No wait a moment
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.46,0:08:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Samu liked {\i1}Takenoko no Sato{\i0}, you got it wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.46,0:08:10.10,TL Note,,0,0,0,,{\pos(954.9,90.6)}TL note: bamboo shoot-shaped and mushroom-shaped chocolate by Meiji\N{\i1}takenoko{\i0} = bamboo shoot | {\i1}kinoko{\i0} = mushroom
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.48,0:08:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It was {\i1}Kinoko no Yama{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.10,0:08:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard it was Choco Baby though
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.10,0:08:13.00,TL Note,,0,0,0,,{\pos(957.6,64.2)}TL note: other Meiji chocolate products
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.82,0:08:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's Apollo
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.10,0:08:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Any will do
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.30,0:08:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like she'll really be able to eat it
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.40,0:08:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,She might be able to in heaven
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.47,0:08:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's heaven, then everything's there
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.87,0:08:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no reason to specially take anything with her going there
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.17,0:08:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I can get anything in heaven?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.17,0:08:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what heaven is after all, you can eat and drink anything
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.37,0:08:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, heaven is above the clouds
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.17,0:08:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way food would be there
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.29,0:08:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Above the clouds?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.99,0:08:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,My grandmother told me the people above that have nothing there just watch us, the ones below
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.62,0:08:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Always?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.13,0:08:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,While snickering, they watch our daily lives
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.37,0:08:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,All day long?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.10,0:08:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Rather than a day, more like year-long?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.27,0:08:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldnt be able to do that if that was me
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.40,0:08:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that just hell then?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.91,0:08:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Those kinds of feelings would disappear, if you're in heaven
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.65,0:08:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Like being paralyzed?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.45,0:09:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, like being given anesthesia
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.37,0:09:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Anesthesia?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.49,0:09:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow, heaven feels scary
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.60,0:09:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Please help yourselves to the food
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.20,0:09:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much\N-Take your time
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.74,0:09:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I kinda feel sorry for looking like we came here to eat
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.78,0:09:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But not eating would be rude too
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.35,0:09:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We really are hungry after all
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.38,0:09:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.18,0:09:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I won't be drinking
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.82,0:09:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Sumi, could you pass the orange juice?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.32,0:09:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know alcohol was a no-go for you
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.72,0:10:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Was the person awhile ago Samu's brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.08,0:10:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.85,0:10:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't he kinda cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.25,0:10:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought so too
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.57,0:10:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,A handsome guy with defined features
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.99,0:10:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like a beard would fit him right?\N-Definitely
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.65,0:10:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Like Mouri Kogoro
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.39,0:10:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A moustache?\N-I was thinking more of on the chin
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.60,0:10:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Like (Daisuke) Jigen's?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.27,0:10:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No, shorter than that
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.30,0:10:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, (Vinsmoke) Sanji's?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.24,0:10:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the one where it's connected from side to chin
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.41,0:10:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Like Heidi's grandpa
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.74,0:10:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a big beard, plus his hair's white
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.61,0:10:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Like that but black
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.78,0:10:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You must like those types a lot Ari
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.12,0:10:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I get what you mean
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.89,0:10:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ari's always been attracted by looks alone
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.42,0:10:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I like those that have really big beards
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.00,0:10:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were to tell the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.43,0:10:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have an interest in boys
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.37,0:11:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep your hands in sync
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.15,0:11:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll be checking on each one of you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.69,0:11:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Keeping up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.82,0:11:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's try it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.33,0:11:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard isn't it?\N-Yeah, it is
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.96,0:11:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice and easy okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.07,0:11:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd find myself looking at girls ever since I was a kid
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.27,0:11:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,My romantic delusions also involved girls
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.84,0:11:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought to myself that it was weird, so I kept it a secret from others
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.62,0:11:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's proceed to the next cut\N- Got it
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.49,0:11:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Then for the next cut, hold on to Samu who will be in the middle,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.49,0:11:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and then Kimu to Momo,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.63,0:12:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and Ari to Sumi, hug your partner from behind
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.02,0:12:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ari go to your position too
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.30,0:12:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Get closer
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.34,0:12:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on tight
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.66,0:12:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.40,0:12:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it fine if we switch places?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.90,0:12:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really mind
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.67,0:12:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,There
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.85,0:12:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.82,0:12:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. I might sweat a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.65,0:13:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.39,0:13:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Sumi's feeling sick
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.82,0:13:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,She's getting feverish
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.29,0:13:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You should get some rest
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.92,0:15:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,How is she? I brought a fever pad
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.49,0:15:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Still sleeping
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.66,0:15:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She looks like she's in pain
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.43,0:15:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.14,0:15:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking at her closely, Sumi really is pretty right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.74,0:15:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Her face is small, and her eyelashes are long after all
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.71,0:15:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.07,0:16:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Komiyama-san still can't come
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.24,0:16:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He's always away when he's needed
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.37,0:16:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.54,0:16:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought "So Samu was the same"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.38,0:16:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I also kept that as a secret
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.86,0:16:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, could we talk for a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.43,0:16:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.39,0:16:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Come over here
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.41,0:16:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.58,0:16:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,is what happened awhile ago like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.08,0:16:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,By that you mean..?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.95,0:16:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What you did to Sumi
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.55,0:16:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The kiss
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.26,0:16:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I did kiss her
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.93,0:16:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you like that too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.10,0:17:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Like that..?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.37,0:17:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You like women..?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.54,0:17:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I have to answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.01,0:17:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If possible, I'd like you to
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.32,0:17:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.92,0:17:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.32,0:17:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The LGBT give off a fashionable sense right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.70,0:17:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it would've been better if I was
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.77,0:17:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impossible
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.27,0:17:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,My heart doesn't go crazy for girls
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.37,0:17:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I have always worried that I am weird
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.21,0:17:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That being found out spelled the end for me
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.96,0:17:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And here she goes talking about fashion sense
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.01,0:17:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that all? Let's go back
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.86,0:18:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,About this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.86,0:18:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell anyone about it
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.53,0:18:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.83,0:18:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It really is impossible
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.73,0:18:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't feel anything at all
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.45,0:18:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,More than a sauce face, shouldn't it be a ketchup face?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.45,0:18:35.72,TL Note,,0,0,0,,{\pos(953.1,115.886)}TL note: sauce face = western(/sharp/defined) facial features\Nketchup face = a little less defined than sauce faces\NSauce in this case is worcestershire, and ketchup is strong but still milder in taste than worcestershire, hence the analogy
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.95,0:18:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ketchup?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.89,0:18:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's strong like sauce, but a little more refreshing
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.79,0:18:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ketchup isn't really refreshing though
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.73,0:18:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,She really was a mysterious girl
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.03,0:18:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Kissing others for no reason
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.90,0:18:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Not thinking about the trouble her strange reasons may cause to the people around her
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.94,0:18:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,At the time of her death, disappearing by the truck's light
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.31,0:18:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Samu was weird right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.01,0:18:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Always doing weird things
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.78,0:18:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought she was pretty cold to us
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.01,0:19:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, Samu can come from {\i1}samui{\i0}(cold)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.35,0:19:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I did say that before
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.09,0:19:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,She will be cremated tomorrow right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.71,0:19:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't remind me
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.63,0:19:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean isn't being burned horrible?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.36,0:19:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Being burned directly in a big incinerator
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.70,0:19:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what do you prefer we do? A burial?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.27,0:19:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,A burial is kinda scary as well, with the feeling of slowly rotting
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.04,0:19:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, a wind funeral?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.94,0:19:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Wind funeral?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.11,0:19:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Let the body be taken by the water, in the end to be eaten by birds and other animals
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.48,0:19:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What? That sounds really scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.35,0:19:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.02,0:19:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitsuhishita san wake up, you'll catch a cold
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.72,0:19:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a rest upstairs
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.63,0:19:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.63,0:19:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.00,0:19:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming, even at this late of a time
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.07,0:19:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Chika's brother
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.34,0:19:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This was...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.14,0:20:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This was...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.91,0:20:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This was...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.22,0:20:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,a very unfortunate passing
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.32,0:20:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It is at this time and going forward
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.56,0:20:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Was there an accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.46,0:20:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,, Yes but actually there are still things to look into
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.37,0:20:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The case is still under police investigation, with regards to it being an accident
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.17,0:20:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What are they still loking into?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.31,0:20:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The truck driver is saying
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.88,0:20:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,that Chika committed suicide
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.68,0:20:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Suicide?
